	<contentText >
		<text  position="relative" width="900px" height="auto" left="0" top="0px" ><![CDATA[Carlos and his colleague, David, have been brought in to service an alarm system. They’re meeting with Gloriana, the company’s IT manager.]]></text>
	</contentText>
